subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: The Jayhawks enter the tournament diminished by the loss of forward Cliff Alexander to an eligibility issue and injuries to Perry Ellis (knee) and Landen Lucas (hip and back).
